Cook sausage in large nonstick skillet over medium-high heat, stirring occasionally, until cooked through. Remove and set aside. Add Spread and green pepper and cook, stirring occasionally, 3 minutes or until tender. Stir in water and Knorr(R) Cajun Sides(TM) - Red Beans & Rice and bring to a boil. Continue boiling over medium heat, stirring occasionally, 10 minutes or until rice and beans are tender. Stir in sausage; heat through.